\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
\begin{document}
}{}$${\rm{C}}{{\rm{V}}_n} = V_n^f-V_n^c$$\end{document}CVn=Vnf−Vnc
where CVn is the change of important climate variables in the ecoregion n; Vjf and Vnc are the future and current climate variables in ecoregion n, respectively.
